@startuml

title Publish-Subscribe Basic Architecture\nEvent distribution through indirect communication

!include ../../../../../../tooling/styles/plantuml/structural/component-diagram-style.iuml

component "Publisher A" as PA #4A90D9
component "Publisher B" as PB #4A90D9

component "Event Bus\n(Pub-Sub Connector)" as EB #F5A623

component "Subscriber 1" as S1 #5BAE5B
component "Subscriber 2" as S2 #5BAE5B
component "Subscriber 3" as S3 #5BAE5B

PA -right-> EB : announce
PB -right-> EB : announce

EB -right-> S1 : deliver
EB -right-> S2 : deliver
EB -right-> S3 : deliver

note bottom of EB
  Publishers and subscribers
  are decoupled - neither knows
  about the other's existence
end note

@enduml

